Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Product

  • public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
    The product class represents the product, with all his attributes. ID is unique for every product.
    Version:
    1.5
    Author:
    Paolo D'Arienzo

        Constructor of Product.
        Parameters:
        ID - is a unique ID for product
        nome - is the name of the product
        numeroPezziDisponibili - is the number of available pieces
        descrizione - is the description of the product
        peso - is the weight of the product
        prezzo - is the price of the product
        classificazione - is the classification of the product
        marca - is the brand of the product
        dataInserimento - is the insertion date of the product
        IPInserimento - is the IP address of the user who added the product
        productType - is the type of product, if normal professional or scholastic
        sconto - is the discount rate
        numeroPezziMinimo - is the minimum number of products needed for getting the discount
        livelloConsigliato - is the suggested level for the instrument
        usato - indicate if the product is used or not
